{{nihongo|'''Toriko Chiya'''|稚野鳥子|Chiya Toriko|lead=yes|born August 25 in [[Tokyo]]}} is a Japanese [[mangaka|manga artist]].<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.manga-news.com/index.php/auteur/CHIYA-Toriko|title= CHIYA Toriko|work= manga-news.com|language= French|accessdate= December 10, 2014}}</ref> She is best known for ''[[Clover (Toriko Chiya manga)|Clover]]'' as well as ''[[Tokyo Alice]]''.<ref name=trefle>{{cite web | url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2012-05-29/toriko-chiya-to-launch-clover-trefle-manga-sequel | title=Toriko Chiya to Launch Clover trèfle Manga Sequel | date=May 29, 2012 | publisher=Anime News Network | accessdate=April 26, 2014}}</ref>

==Works==
* {{nihongo|''Danchi Kaidan Kaidan''|団地階段会談}}<br>(1990, ''Bouquet'', Shueisha, 1 volume)<ref>{{cite web | url=https://mediaarts-db.bunka.go.jp/mg/books/1160448 | script-title=ja:団地階段会談  | publisher=[[Agency for Cultural Affairs]] | website=Media Arts Database | accessdate=January 18, 2018 | language=Japanese}}</ref>
* {{nihongo|''Bara-gara no Hoshī Toshigoro''|薔薇柄の欲しい年頃}}<br>(1991, ''Bouquet'', Shueisha, 2 volumes)<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bookoffonline.co.jp/old/0011420083 | script-title=ja:薔薇柄の欲しい年頃(前) | publisher=BookOffOnline.co.jp | accessdate=April 26, 2014 | language=Japanese}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bookoffonline.co.jp/old/0011420088 | script-title=ja:薔薇柄の欲しい年頃(後) | publisher=BookOffOnline.co.jp | accessdate=April 26, 2014 | language=Japanese}}</ref>
* ''Miracle''<br>(1992–1993, ''Bouquet'', Shueisha, 4 volumes)<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bookoffonline.co.jp/old/0011420104 | title=Miracle(1) | publisher=BookOffOnline.co.jp | accessdate=April 26, 2014 | language=Japanese}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bookoffonline.co.jp/old/0011420135 | title=Miracle(4) | publisher=BookOffOnline.co.jp | accessdate=April 26, 2014 | language=Japanese}}</ref>
* {{nihongo|''Watashi no Ichiban Sukina Hito''|わたしの一番好きな人}}<br>(1993, ''Bouquet'', Shueisha, 1 volume)<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bookoffonline.co.jp/old/0011420591 | script-title=ja:わたしの一番好きな人 | publisher=BookOffOnline.co.jp | accessdate=April 26, 2014 | language=Japanese}}</ref>
* {{nihongo|''Angel ni Kiite''|天使（エンジェル）に聞いて|Enjeru ni Kiite}}<br>(1993–1994, ''Bouquet'', Shueisha, 4 volumes)<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bookoffonline.co.jp/old/0011420603 | script-title=ja:天使に聞いて（ワイド版）(1) | publisher=BookOffOnline.co.jp | accessdate=April 26, 2014 | language=Japanese}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bookoffonline.co.jp/old/0011413653 | script-title=ja:天使に聞いて（ワイド版）(4) | publisher=BookOffOnline.co.jp | accessdate=April 26, 2014 | language=Japanese}}</ref>
* {{nihongo|''Tengoku no Hana''|天国の花}}<br/>(1994–1996, ''Bouquet'', Shueisha, 6 volumes)<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bookoffonline.co.jp/old/0011379957 | script-title=ja:天国の花(1) | publisher=BookOffOnline.co.jp | accessdate=April 26, 2014 | language=Japanese}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bookoffonline.co.jp/old/0011379468 | script-title=ja:天国の花(6) | publisher=BookOffOnline.co.jp | accessdate=April 26, 2014 | language=Japanese}}</ref>
* {{nihongo|''[[Clover (Toriko Chiya manga)|Clover]]''|クローバー|Kurōbā}}<br/>(1997–2010, ''Bouquet''→''[[Cookie (manga magazine)|Cookie]]''→''[[Chorus (magazine)|Chorus]]'', [[Shueisha]], 24 volumes)<ref>{{cite web | url=http://natalie.mu/comic/news/31211 | script-title=ja:稚野鳥子「クローバー」大団円！フェリシモとのコラボも | date=April 28, 2010 | publisher=[[Natalie (website)|Natalie]] | accessdate=April 25, 2014 | language=Japanese}}</ref><ref name=news>{{cite web | url=http://www.manga-news.com/index.php/actus/2010/04/28/Fin-de-Clover | title=Fin de Clover | date=April 28, 2010 | publisher=Manga News | accessdate=April 25, 2014 | language=French}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://books.shueisha.co.jp/CGI/search/zen_list.cgi?siries_isbn=X-08-848687-0&siries_kanren_isbn=&mode=2 | script-title=ja:クローバー ／ 第1巻～第24巻 | publisher=Shueisha | accessdate=April 26, 2014 |language=Japanese }}</ref>
* {{nihongo|''[[Tokyo Alice]]''|東京アリス|Tōkyō Arisu}}<br/>(2005–2015, ''[[Kiss (Japanese magazine)|Kiss]]'', [[Kodansha]], 15 volumes)<ref>{{cite web | url=http://kc.kodansha.co.jp/product?isbn=9784063406092 | script-title=ja:東京アリス (1) | publisher=[[Kodansha]] | accessdate=January 18, 2018 | language=Japanese}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://kc.kodansha.co.jp/product?isbn=9784063409673 | script-title=ja:東京アリス (15) | publisher=Kodansha | accessdate=January 18, 2018 | language=Japanese}}</ref>
* {{nihongo|''Kazoku Switch''|家族スイッチ|Kazoku Suitchi}}<br/>(2010–2012, ''Chorus''→''Cocohana'', Shueisha, 4 volumes)<ref>{{cite web | url=https://natalie.mu/comic/news/33924 | script-title=ja:稚野鳥子「クローバー」のお洋服がフェリシモから発売 | publisher=Natalie | accessdate=January 18, 2018 |language=Japanese }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-11-28/lineup-revealed-for-shueisha-cocohana-magazine | title=Shueisha's Cocohana Magazine Manga Lineup Revealed | date=November 28, 2011 | publisher=Anime News Network | accessdate=April 25, 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://books.shueisha.co.jp:80/CGI/search/syousai_put.cgi?isbn_cd=978-4-08-846794-8 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108103023/http://books.shueisha.co.jp/CGI/search/syousai_put.cgi?isbn_cd=978-4-08-846794-8 | archivedate=November 8, 2012 | title=家族スイッチ 4 | publisher=Shueisha | language=Japanese | deadurl=yes | df= }}</ref>
* {{nihongo|''Clover trèfle''|クローバー trefle(トレフル)|Kurōbā Torefuru}}<br/>(2012–ongoing, ''Cocohana'', Shueisha, 8 volumes)<ref name=trefle/><ref>{{cite web | url=http://books.shueisha.co.jp/CGI/search/zen_list.cgi?siries_isbn=X78-4-08-846885-3&siries_kanren_isbn=&mode=2 | title= クローバー　trefle／ 第1巻～第3巻 | publisher=Shueisha | accessdate=January 18, 2018 |language=Japanese }}</ref>
* {{nihongo|''Tsuki to Yubisaki no Aida''<!-- romanization according to the Kodansha site -->|月と指先の間}}<br/>(2015–ongoing, ''Kiss'', Kodansha, 3 volumes)<ref>{{cite web | url=http://kc.kodansha.co.jp/product?isbn=9784063774306 | script-title=ja:月と指先の間 (1) | publisher=Kodansha | accessdate=January 18, 2018 | language=Japanese}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://kc.kodansha.co.jp/title?code=1000027026 | script-title=ja:月と指先の間 | publisher=Kodansha | accessdate=January 18, 2018 | language=Japanese}}</ref>

